nk is smart is that <a href=\"https:\/\/www.made.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">MADE.com<\/a> throws in links to some of the specific products that were featured as well as a link to information on their interior design service at the bottom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"428\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-1024x428.png\" alt=\"Product Page\" class=\"wp-image-89961\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-1024x428.png 1024w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-300x125.png 300w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-768x321.png 768w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-380x159.png 380w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-600x251.png 600w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-760x318.png 760w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-84x35.png 84w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-120x50.png 120w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-740x309.png 740w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-220x92.png 220w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2-385x161.png 385w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image35-2.png 1359w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.made.com\/inspiration\/less-is-more-minimalism-with-flair-in-a-parisian-apartment\"><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a subtle, non-pushy way to promote their products and services while highlighting them in a very natural way. So with just a click, a shopper can find a product they\u2019re interested in, like the Indi ceramic bowl, and make a purchase.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"428\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-1024x428.png\" alt=\"Product Called Indi\" class=\"wp-image-89873\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-1024x428.png 1024w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-300x125.png 300w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-768x321.png 768w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-380x159.png 380w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-600x251.png 600w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-760x318.png 760w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-84x35.png 84w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-120x50.png 120w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-740x309.png 740w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-220x92.png 220w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18-385x161.png 385w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image13-18.png 1361w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>And that\u2019s really what e-commerce content marketing is all about\u2014providing shoppers with genuine value, while at the same time promoting your products for a win-win.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So I think there\u2019s a lot to be learned from MADE.com\u2019s campaign.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Lunya<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.lunya.co\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Lunya<\/a> is a sleepwear company that specifically makes products for women.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"427\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image38-3-1024x427.png\" alt=\"Lunya Homemade\" class=\"wp-image-89973\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image38-3-1024x427.png 1024w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image38-3-300x125.png 300w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image38-3-768x320.png 768w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image38-3-380x158.png 380w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image38-3-600x250.png 600w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image38-3-760x317.png 760w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image38-3-84x35.png 84w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image38-3-120x50.png 120w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-