>This shows that you can take a conventional content medium like a blog post and get super creative with it.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For even more cool ideas, I suggest browsing through the rest of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.lunya.co\/blogs\/our-bedroom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Lunya blog<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>DockATot<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is an e-commerce brand that sells a \u201cmulti-functional lounging, playing, chilling, resting, and snuggling dock for babies and tots.\u201d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"430\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-1024x430.png\" alt=\"Dock A Tot\" class=\"wp-image-89921\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-1024x430.png 1024w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-300x126.png 300w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-768x322.png 768w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-380x160.png 380w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-600x252.png 600w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-760x319.png 760w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-83x35.png 83w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-119x50.png 119w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-740x311.png 740w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-220x92.png 220w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7-385x162.png 385w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image25-7.png 1360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/dockatot.com\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>DockATot\u2019s aim is to provide quality products that offer many benefits that similar competitors do not, such as using zero harmful substances and being Oeko-Tex Certified.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"429\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image18-16-1024x429.png\" alt=\"Dock A Tot Collections\" class=\"wp-image-89893\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image18-16-1024x429.png 1024w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image18-16-300x126.png 300w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image18-16-768x322.png 768w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image18-16-380x159.png 380w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image18-16-600x252.png 600w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image18-16-760x319.png 760w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image18-16-83x35.png 83w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image18-16-119x50.png 119w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image18-16-740x310.png 740w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202