ds\/2020\/04\/image21-1-385x684.jpg 385w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/dockatot.com\/blogs\/news\/a-toddler-gift-guide-by-alex-elle\"><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then, Alex features a numbered list of products, including items like toddler soap, a pacifier, books, rain boots, diapers, wipes, and so on.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on a link, and a reader is instantly taken to each individual product page like this one from Dr. Bronner\u2019s Castile Soap.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"429\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-1024x429.png\" alt=\"Pure Soap\" class=\"wp-image-89945\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-1024x429.png 1024w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-300x126.png 300w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-768x322.png 768w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-380x159.png 380w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-600x251.png 600w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-760x319.png 760w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-84x35.png 84w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-119x50.png 119w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-740x310.png 740w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/image31-4-220x92.png 220w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2ad